title: Ubuntu 22.04.4 LTS (Jammy Jellyfish) Released with Linux Kernel 6.5, Mesa 23.2
description:
Ubuntu 22.04.4 LTS (Jammy Jellyfish) distribution is now available for download with Linux kernel 6.5 from Ubuntu 23.10 (Mantic Minotaur), Mesa 23.2, as well as various other updated components.

title: LibreOffice 7.6.5 Office Suite Is Out Now with More Than 90 Bug Fixes
description:

title: KDE Slimbook V Is the World’s First Linux Laptop to Ship with KDE Plasma 6
description:
